sp.p:
Why, we shall move off to quod if we don't look out;

 so we must make a good haul at once, and then do for our— what the beaks would
       like to do for us.

Many gals despises a man, but they falls in love with, and marries the canary birds;
       although very often after marriage they soon gets tired of the music. Last time of asking,
       will you marry—
